<A>__{zeke and dave as they beat one another on the back.}
<C>__{dave}
<D>__{whar you been all these months?}
<C>__{zeke}
<D>__{up in the hills workin' my way down the biggest hole you ever seed.}
<C>__{dave}
<D>__{good what's at the bottom of it?}
<C>__{zeke}
<D>__{nothin'!}
<C>__{dave}
<P>__{(roaring with laughter)}
<D>__{what, again!!}
<B>__{med. shot}
<A>__{rocklin has entered and moved to the fire. miss martin and clara enter and stand in the doorway watching the scene at the bar. a pale faced, dyspeptic looking man of about 45 (stan) comes from the kitchen and approaches them ingratiatingly.}
<C>__{stan}
<D>__{good evening, ladies. how about something to eat?}
