<P>__{(with a dubious look}
<D>__{toward the pair at}
<P>__{the bar)}
<D>__{well if it won't take too long.}
<C>__{stan}
<P>__{(leading the way toward the partition)}
<D>__{this way, ladies.}
<B>__{med. close shot}
<A>__{bar. dave has just fitted a cylindrical record of "she was only a bird in a gilded cage" to an old type phonograph.}
<C>__{dave}
<D>__{yep this is my last trip.}
<C>__{zeke}
<D>__{why?}
<C>__{dave}
